&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with stakeholders to devise metrics to identify areas for improvement to reduce our mean time for issue resolution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Suggest architecture improvements that improve the reliability of our platform and maintain our market leadership&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
