&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Inspire the team to take responsibility for their delivery process and the outcomes they deliver, focus them on delivering value or failing fast.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Facilitate or remove impediments to delivery and waste in our processes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
